<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.155782>
    dc:description "FIGURES 1 ┬Ł 5. Mouthparts of Microlia meticola (Casey) (Arizona). 1 ŌĆō labrum; 2 ŌĆō epipharynx; 3 ŌĆō left mandible, dorsal view; 4 ŌĆō left mandible, ventral view; 5 ŌĆō right mandible, dorsal view. Scale bar 0.1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/155782/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.155783>
    dc:description "FIGURES 21 ┬Ł 25. Abdominal segment 8 and female accessory sclerites of Microlia silacea (Erichson) (21 ŌĆō paralectotype of Homalota silacea; 22, 25 ŌĆō North Carolina; 23 ┬Ł 24 ŌĆō lectotype of Homalota silacea). 21 ŌĆō male sternum 8; 22 ŌĆō male tergum 8; 23 ŌĆō female sternum 8; 24 ŌĆō female tergum 8; 25 ŌĆō female accessory sclerites. Scale bar 0.25 mm (21 ┬Ł 24), 0.1 mm (25)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/155783/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.155784>
    dc:description "FIGURES 26 ┬Ł 33. Details of Microlia silacea (Erichson) (26 ┬Ł 29, 31 ŌĆō paralectotype of Homalota silacea; 30, 33 ŌĆō North Carolina; 32 ŌĆō lectotype of Homalota silacea). 26 ŌĆō median lobe of aedeagus, lateral view; 27 ŌĆō apex of median lobe of aedeagus, lateral view; 28 ŌĆō median lobe of aedeagus, ventral view; 29 ŌĆō apex of median lobe of aedeagus, ventral view; 30 ŌĆō antenna; 31 ŌĆō apical lobe of right paramere, internal view; 32 ┬Ł 33 ŌĆō spermatheca. Scale bar 0.2 mm (25, 27, 29, 31 ┬Ł 33), 0.1 mm (26, 28, 30)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/155784/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.155785>
    dc:description "FIGURES 34 ┬Ł 37. Details of Microlia meticola (Casey) (Arizona). 34 ŌĆō male sternum 8; 35 ŌĆō male tergum 8; 36 ŌĆō female sternum 8; 37 ŌĆō female tergum 8. Scale bar 0.4 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/155785/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.155786>
    dc:description "FIGURES 38 ┬Ł 44. Details of Microlia meticola (Casey) (Arizona). 38 ŌĆō median lobe of aedeagus, lateral view; 39 ŌĆō apex of median lobe of aedeagus, lateral view; 40 ŌĆō median lobe of aedeagus, ventral view; 41 ŌĆō apex of median lobe of aedeagus, ventral view; 42 ┬Ł 43 ŌĆō spermatheca; 44 ŌĆō apical lobe of right paramere, internal view. Scale bar 0.2 mm (38, 40, 42 ┬Ł 43), 0.1 mm (39, 41, 44)." ;
