<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.155787>
    dc:description "FIGURES 45 ┬Ł 48. Details of Microlia azteca (Casey) (paralectotype). 45 ŌĆō female sternum 8; 46 ŌĆō female tergum 8; 47 ŌĆō spermatheca; 48 ŌĆō right antenna. Scale bar 0.2 mm." ;
