<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.155789>
    dc:description "FIGURES 53 ┬Ł 61. Details of Microlia pentamera Gusarov, sp. nov. (53 ┬Ł 58, 61 ŌĆō holotype; 59 ┬Ł 60 ŌĆō paratypes). 53 ŌĆō median lobe of aedeagus, lateral view; 54 ŌĆō apex of median lobe of aedeagus, lateral view; 55 ŌĆō median lobe of aedeagus, ventral view; 56 ŌĆō apex of median lobe of aedeagus, ventral view; 57 ŌĆō copulatory piece of internal sac; 58 ŌĆō apical lobe of right paramere, internal view; 59 ┬Ł 60 ŌĆō spermatheca; 61 ŌĆō abdominal segment 3, dorsal view. Scale bar 0.2 mm (53, 55, 59 ┬Ł 60), 0.1 mm (54, 56 ┬Ł 58), 0.55 mm (61)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/155789/files/figure.png" ;
