<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.155790>
    dc:description "FIGURES 62 ┬Ł 67. Details of Microlia tetramera Gusarov, sp. nov. (62 ┬Ł 63 ŌĆō holotype; 64 ┬Ł 67 ŌĆō possible female of M. tetramera from Costa Rica, 64 ┬Ł 65 ŌĆō type A, 66 ┬Ł 67 ŌĆō type B). 62 ŌĆō male sternum 8; 63 ŌĆō male tergum 8; 64, 66 ŌĆō female sternum 8; 65, 67 ŌĆō female tergum 8. Scale bar 0.2 mm." ;
