    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.155791>
    dc:description "FIGURES 68 ┬Ł 76. Details of Microlia tetramera Gusarov, sp. nov. (68 ┬Ł 72, 75 ┬Ł 76 ŌĆō holotype; 73 ┬Ł 74 ŌĆō possible female of M. tetramera from Costa Rica). 68 ŌĆō median lobe of aedeagus, lateral view; 69 ŌĆō apex of median lobe of aedeagus, lateral view; 70 ŌĆō median lobe of aedeagus, ventral view; 71 ŌĆō apex of median lobe of aedeagus, ventral view; 72 ŌĆō apex of median lobe of aedeagus, apical ventral view; 73 ┬Ł 74 ŌĆō spermatheca; 75 ŌĆō apical lobe of right paramere, internal view; 76 ŌĆō abdominal segment 3, dorsal view. Scale bar 0.2 mm (68, 70, 73 ┬Ł 74), 0.1 mm (69, 71 ┬Ł 72, 75), 0.55 mm (76)." ;
